1) Go on store page for this game (if you aren't already there);
2) Scroll down to reviews;
3) Choose Positive only" tab;
4) Press "Load more reviews" on the bottom of the page;
5) Look for reviewers with 1 review on account and low amount of products on account (3 or less);
6) Open some of these accounts: either no playtime("0.1h on record") in the game or actively idling ("Recent Game Activity" = "total time on the record in this game").
